<c.bg_transparent>Discipline this!</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:23:48.677 --> 00:23:49.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles!</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:23:49.719 --> 00:23:50.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:23:53.682 --> 00:23:54.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be quiet!</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:23:59.062 --> 00:24:01.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: That's one Black Hole</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>straight up, right?</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:24:03.191 --> 00:24:04.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Synthale, please.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:24:05.318 --> 00:24:06.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be right with you, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:24:17.998 --> 00:24:19.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quark, what about that synthale?</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:24:19.666 --> 00:24:20.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just another minute.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:24:25.755 --> 00:24:26.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quark?</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:24:27.090 --> 00:24:29.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, Chief, I'm a little busy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>right now.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:24:32.387 --> 00:24:34.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm in no mood for games, Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:24:34.514 --> 00:24:36.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So why don't you give me my drink</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:24:36.683 --> 00:24:39.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>or I break every bone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in your worthless little body.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:24:39.853 --> 00:24:42.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, just because your life's</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in shambles right now--</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:24:42.689 --> 00:24:44.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:24:45.192 --> 00:24:47.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One synthale coming right up.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:24:48.236 --> 00:24:49.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:25:16.765 --> 00:25:17.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles?</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:25:19.517 --> 00:25:20.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:25:21.561 --> 00:25:25.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I've never really been gone, have I?</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:25:27.442 --> 00:25:28.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not real.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:25:29.361 --> 00:25:30.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're just in my head.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:25:31.071 --> 00:25:32.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's all I ever was.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:25:33.949 --> 00:25:36.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I'm real to you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and that's all that matters.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:25:37.619 --> 00:25:38.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go away.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:25:39.246 --> 00:25:43.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm your friend. You need me.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:25:43.833 --> 00:25:46.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the last thing I need.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:25:46.086 --> 00:25:49.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're wrong, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You need me, now more than ever.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:26:18.702 --> 00:26:19.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:26:20.704 --> 00:26:21.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to work.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:26:22.622 --> 00:26:28.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, as your friend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have to tell you I'm worried about you.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:26:32.966 --> 00:26:35.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be. I'm home.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:26:35.844 --> 00:26:36.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm working</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:26:37.345 --> 00:26:39.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and for the first time in as long</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as I can remember</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:26:39.973 --> 00:26:40.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel good.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:26:42.225 --> 00:26:43.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why am I here?</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:26:43.393 --> 00:26:46.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sisko to O'Brien.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Please report to my office.</i></c.bg_transparent>

362
00:26:46.521 --> 00:26:47.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On my way.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:26:48.732 --> 00:26:49.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, I don't know why you're here</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:26:51.067 --> 00:26:52.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I don't care.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:27:06.333 --> 00:27:07.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have a seat.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:27:15.175 --> 00:27:19.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand you had a confrontation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Dr. Bashir yesterday.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:27:20.013 --> 00:27:21.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that's a...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That was nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:27:21.890 --> 00:27:23.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not according to Dr. Bashir.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:27:24.017 --> 00:27:27.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We had a little argument.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Julian and I are always arguing.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:27:27.604 --> 00:27:30.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to Constable Odo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you also had an incident with Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:27:31.316 --> 00:27:32.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did that little?</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:27:34.903 --> 00:27:38.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, sir, I may have let things get</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little out of hand, but...</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:27:38.823 --> 00:27:39.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't happen again.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:27:40.158 --> 00:27:40.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm...</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:27:41.785 --> 00:27:44.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Bashir also tells me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you've stopped seeing your counselor.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:27:45.789 --> 00:27:47.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, I've been very busy lately--</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:27:47.248 --> 00:27:49.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The agreement was that you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were going to see a counselor</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:27:49.709 --> 00:27:50.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a regular basis.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:27:52.295 --> 00:27:53.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're right.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:27:53.630 --> 00:27:55.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll make an appointment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to go see him tomorrow.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:27:55.882 --> 00:27:57.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll see him today.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:27:58.593 --> 00:27:59.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:28:00.720 --> 00:28:02.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have a lot of work to do today, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:28:02.514 --> 00:28:03.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The work can wait.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:28:05.767 --> 00:28:07.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As of now, you're relieved of duty.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:28:08.395 --> 00:28:10.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to report to Counselor Telnorri</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:28:10.688 --> 00:28:12.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and begin attending</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>daily counseling sessions</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:28:13.316 --> 00:28:15.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for as long as he thinks it's advisable.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:28:16.403 --> 00:28:18.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, you're blowing this all</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out of proportion.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:28:18.988 --> 00:28:20.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know that's not true.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:28:20.907 --> 00:28:22.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to you on Argratha</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:28:22.784 --> 00:28:24.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>affected you a lot more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than you're willing to admit</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:28:25.328 --> 00:28:27.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it's not going to get better overnight</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:28:27.205 --> 00:28:28.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>no matter how much you want it to.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:28:29.833 --> 00:28:30.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need help.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:28:32.127 --> 00:28:33.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:28:34.546 --> 00:28:39.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you as a personal favor to me.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Give me one more chance.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:28:42.345 --> 00:28:43.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I could.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:28:45.932 --> 00:28:46.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But right now</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:28:47.100 --> 00:28:50.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in the judgment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this station's Chief Medical Officer</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:28:50.520 --> 00:28:54.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you're unfit for duty</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>which means you're on medical leave</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:28:54.607 --> 00:28:55.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>effective immediately</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:28:55.942 --> 00:28:58.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and if you don't begin attending</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>counseling sessions</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:28:58.653 --> 00:28:59.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a regular basis</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:28:59.821 --> 00:29:02.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and cooperating in every</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>other way with your physician</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:29:02.866 --> 00:29:04.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will have no choice</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:29:04.284 --> 00:29:06.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but to have you confined</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:29:06.619 --> 00:29:07.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that clear?</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:29:09.205 --> 00:29:10.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:29:13.626 --> 00:29:14.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dismissed.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:29:24.721 --> 00:29:27.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, I was just about to head down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Replimat...</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:29:27.766 --> 00:29:29.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not now, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:29:32.479 --> 00:29:33.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Promenade.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:29:41.696 --> 00:29:43.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What the hell did you say to him?</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:29:43.615 --> 00:29:45.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take it you talked to Captain Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:29:45.492 --> 00:29:46.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I talked to him, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:29:47.035 --> 00:29:49.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He relieved me of duty.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's for the best, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:29:49.871 --> 00:29:51.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know what's best for me?</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:29:52.373 --> 00:29:54.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have no idea what I've been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>going through!</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:29:54.375 --> 00:29:57.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're right. You were alone in that cell.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I wasn't there with you.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:29:57.587 --> 00:30:00.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't see what they did to you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I do know you suffered</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:30:00.256 --> 00:30:02.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and that you're still suffering now,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm trying to help.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:30:03.009 --> 00:30:04.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never asked for your help.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:30:04.886 --> 00:30:08.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You didn't need to ask.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm your doctor and your friend.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:30:08.848 --> 00:30:10.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>EE'CHAR: You should listen to him, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:30:10.809 --> 00:30:13.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He cares about you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just like I did.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:30:13.269 --> 00:30:15.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't make the same mistake with him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you did with me.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:30:17.774 --> 00:30:19.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you get it?</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:30:19.984 --> 00:30:22.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not my friend! Not anymore!</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:30:23.655 --> 00:30:26.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The O'Brien that was your friend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>died in that cell!</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:30:26.658 --> 00:30:27.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not dead.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:30:28.785 --> 00:30:30.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He just needs a little help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's all.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:30:31.579 --> 00:30:32.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stay away from me.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:30:33.915 --> 00:30:36.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want your help,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want your friendship</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:30:36.876 --> 00:30:38.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just want to be left alone!</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:30:42.173 --> 00:30:44.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where are you going?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I told you to go away!</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:30:44.425 --> 00:30:47.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, please, don't do this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Go back there and talk to him.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:30:47.887 --> 00:30:48.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He wants to help you.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:30:48.972 --> 00:30:50.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Like you did?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:30:50.974 --> 00:30:54.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We're both your friends.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah, and look what happened to you.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:30:54.936 --> 00:30:55.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Habitat Ring.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:31:03.486 --> 00:31:06.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, sooner or later</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll have to tell someone about me.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:31:06.656 --> 00:31:07.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like hell I will.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:31:09.117 --> 00:31:11.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't run from me forever.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:31:12.912 --> 00:31:13.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're dead</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:31:14.163 --> 00:31:16.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so why don't you go away</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and leave me alone?</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:31:16.833 --> 00:31:18.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want me to leave?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll leave!</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:31:19.002 --> 00:31:20.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Send me away!</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:31:20.670 --> 00:31:21.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:31:21.963 --> 00:31:25.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I keep coming back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's because some part of you</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:31:25.174 --> 00:31:26.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>keeps bringing me here!</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:31:42.317 --> 00:31:44.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, Julian's been trying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to contact you for an hour.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:31:45.028 --> 00:31:47.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where have you been?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Walking. Thinking.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:31:47.906 --> 00:31:50.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know. I heard. I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:31:50.867 --> 00:31:54.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I know how much your work means to you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Try telling that to Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:31:55.455 --> 00:31:57.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy, come see what I drew.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:31:58.458 --> 00:32:01.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Not now, honey, okay?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm sure it's only temporary.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:32:01.544 --> 00:32:03.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be back at work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before you know it.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:32:03.338 --> 00:32:04.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy, you have to come see.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:32:05.214 --> 00:32:06.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, can we talk about this later?</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:32:07.050 --> 00:32:08.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Daddy, come on!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Not now.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:32:08.968 --> 00:32:11.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Please, Daddy, please!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I said not now, right?</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:32:11.888 --> 00:32:13.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I said not!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Miles! What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:32:15.725 --> 00:32:17.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, shh, shh.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:32:20.855 --> 00:32:21.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't mean to...</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:32:21.981 --> 00:32:23.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shh.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:32:25.026 --> 00:32:26.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:33:51.320 --> 00:33:52.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief?</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:33:55.867 --> 00:33:57.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get out of here, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:33:59.328 --> 00:34:01.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want to do this, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:34:02.582 --> 00:34:03.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The hell I don't.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:34:06.544 --> 00:34:09.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, I don't claim to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you're going through</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:34:09.088 --> 00:34:11.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but whatever it is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's not worth dying for.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:34:14.594 --> 00:34:16.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand at all.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:34:18.514 --> 00:34:19.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not doing this for me.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:34:21.100 --> 00:34:26.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm doing it to protect Keiko and Molly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and everyone else in this station.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:34:26.606 --> 00:34:28.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Protect us from what?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-From me.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:34:32.028 --> 00:34:34.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not the man I used to be.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:34:35.615 --> 00:34:37.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm dangerous.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:34:41.579 --> 00:34:42.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I nearly hit Molly today.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:34:44.082 --> 00:34:45.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All she wanted was a little attention</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:34:46.918 --> 00:34:48.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I nearly hit her.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:34:49.670 --> 00:34:50.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you didn't.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:34:53.049 --> 00:34:55.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a good man, Miles Edward O'Brien</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:34:56.844 --> 00:34:58.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and whatever it is you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've done wrong</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:34:58.930 --> 00:35:00.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you don't deserve to die.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:35:00.765 --> 00:35:02.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sound like Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:35:03.059 --> 00:35:04.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who's Ee'Char?</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:35:07.188 --> 00:35:10.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's... not real.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:35:14.070 --> 00:35:15.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's just a memory, that's all.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:35:16.531 --> 00:35:18.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A memory from Argratha?</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:35:19.492 --> 00:35:22.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who was he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Another prisoner? A guard?</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:35:23.621 --> 00:35:25.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was my cell mate.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:35:26.290 --> 00:35:28.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You told me you were alone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in that cell.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:35:28.835 --> 00:35:30.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Twenty years with no one to talk to.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:35:38.302 --> 00:35:44.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was at the end, a week... two maybe.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:35:47.061 --> 00:35:48.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But the rest of the time...</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:35:50.398 --> 00:35:51.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:35:53.985 --> 00:35:55.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to him?</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:35:59.949 --> 00:36:01.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( distant yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:36:01.784 --> 00:36:02.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah...</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:36:03.202 --> 00:36:04.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why'd you do that?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:36:10.877 --> 00:36:11.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't helping.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:36:13.337 --> 00:36:15.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need to concentrate more.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:36:15.423 --> 00:36:19.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't matter how much I concentrate.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm still starving.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:36:20.720 --> 00:36:22.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:36:23.055 --> 00:36:24.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So am I.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:36:25.558 --> 00:36:27.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sure there's nothing left?</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:36:27.560 --> 00:36:30.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not unless you have a hiding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>place I don't know about.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:36:30.771 --> 00:36:33.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We ate the last of the food</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I put away a week ago.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:36:36.611 --> 00:36:38.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should have stockpiled more.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:36:39.447 --> 00:36:41.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should have prepared for this.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:36:41.741 --> 00:36:44.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They've never let us go this long</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without food before.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:36:45.077 --> 00:36:50.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe they've forgotten about us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or just decided to finally let us die.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:36:54.086 --> 00:36:55.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then we die.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:36:56.130 --> 00:36:58.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARGRATHI: ( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>over PA </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>) </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>All offenders</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>prepare for dormancy period.</i></c.bg_transparent>

517
00:36:59.217 --> 00:37:01.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Any offender still active</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>during the dormancy period</i></c.bg_transparent>

518
00:37:01.886 --> 00:37:02.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>will be disciplined.</i></c.bg_transparent>

519
00:37:03.054 --> 00:37:06.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Illumination will be suspended</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>in 20 seconds.</i></c.bg_transparent>

520
00:37:07.558 --> 00:37:08.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:37:09.310 --> 00:37:10.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to sleep.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:37:10.895 --> 00:37:15.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How can you sleep at a time like this?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Maybe I'll dream about food.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:37:17.610 --> 00:37:18.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're crazy.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:37:19.028 --> 00:37:19.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No...</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:37:21.405 --> 00:37:22.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just hungry.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:37:23.616 --> 00:37:25.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARGRATHI: ( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>over PA </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i></i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dormancy period initiated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

527
00:38:18.671 --> 00:38:19.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:38:23.592 --> 00:38:25.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You pretended to be my friend</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:38:25.970 --> 00:38:28.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and all the time you were holding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out on me.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:38:28.472 --> 00:38:30.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now who's acting crazy?</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:38:36.856 --> 00:38:40.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After everything I've done for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you ungrateful...</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:38:56.167 --> 00:38:57.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( bones crunching )</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:39:09.889 --> 00:39:11.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:39:12.350 --> 00:39:13.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You...</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:39:14.727 --> 00:39:17.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were saving it for both of us.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:39:24.737 --> 00:39:25.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:39:28.532 --> 00:39:30.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char, wake up.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:39:42.380 --> 00:39:44.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char... Ee'Char...</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:39:47.176 --> 00:39:48.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You killed him?</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:39:52.890 --> 00:39:54.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The worst part of it was...</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:39:55.309 --> 00:39:59.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The next day, the guards</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>began feeding me again.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:40:01.774 --> 00:40:03.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I killed him for nothing,</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:40:04.402 --> 00:40:06.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for a scrap of bread</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he was going to share with me.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:40:07.696 --> 00:40:09.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it was a mistake. You didn't mean it.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:40:12.701 --> 00:40:13.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I meant it.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:40:15.162 --> 00:40:16.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted him to die.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:40:19.250 --> 00:40:20.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I keep telling myself...</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:40:22.420 --> 00:40:23.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:40:23.838 --> 00:40:25.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't real.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:40:25.840 --> 00:40:26.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But that's a lie.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:40:28.008 --> 00:40:29.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it had been real, if it had been you</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:40:29.969 --> 00:40:31.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>instead of him</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:40:31.595 --> 00:40:33.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it wouldn't have made any difference.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:40:34.432 --> 00:40:38.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was my best friend and I murdered him.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:40:40.980 --> 00:40:43.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When we were growing up,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they used to tell us...</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:40:44.900 --> 00:40:46.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Humanity had evolved</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:40:48.070 --> 00:40:52.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that mankind had outgrown hate and rage.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:40:55.703 --> 00:40:57.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But when it came down to it</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:40:58.289 --> 00:41:03.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I had the chance to show</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that no matter what anyone did to me</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:41:03.127 --> 00:41:05.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was still an evolved human being...</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:41:08.174 --> 00:41:09.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I failed.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:41:12.553 --> 00:41:15.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I repaid kindness with blood.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:41:19.643 --> 00:41:21.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was no better than an animal.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:41:22.104 --> 00:41:23.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. No, no, no.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:41:23.647 --> 00:41:25.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>An animal would've killed Ee'Char</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:41:25.232 --> 00:41:28.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and never had a second thought,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>never shed a tear</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:41:28.486 --> 00:41:30.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but not you. You hate yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:41:31.530 --> 00:41:34.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You hate yourself so much you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you deserve to die.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:41:35.326 --> 00:41:38.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Argrathi did everything they could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to strip you of your humanity</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:41:39.663 --> 00:41:42.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and in the end, for one brief moment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they succeeded.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:41:43.584 --> 00:41:46.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you can't let that brief moment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>define your entire life.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:41:47.546 --> 00:41:52.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you do, if you pull that trigger</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then the Argrathi will have won.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:41:53.260 --> 00:41:59.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They will have destroyed a good man.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You cannot let that happen, my friend.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:42:14.198 --> 00:42:15.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:42:17.618 --> 00:42:18.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be well, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:42:44.728 --> 00:42:47.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thirty milligrams twice a day.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Take it religiously for a month.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:42:47.106 --> 00:42:49.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And if all goes well</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll experiment with a lower dosage.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:42:49.233 --> 00:42:50.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sure this'll work?</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:42:50.276 --> 00:42:53.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a treatment, not a cure.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It'll prevent hallucinations</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:42:53.612 --> 00:42:55.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>take the edge off the depression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but that's all it'll do.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:42:55.739 --> 00:42:57.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't take away the memories</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or the feelings.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:42:57.950 --> 00:42:59.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean the guilt.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:42:59.618 --> 00:43:01.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, that'll take time.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:43:02.997 --> 00:43:04.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now's the part where you tell me</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:43:04.999 --> 00:43:06.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to start seeing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Counselor Telnorri again.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:43:07.793 --> 00:43:09.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unless you want to talk to me.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:43:10.462 --> 00:43:11.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Telnorri'll be fine.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:43:17.511 --> 00:43:19.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks, Julian... For everything.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:43:20.556 --> 00:43:21.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are friends for?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:43:31.567 --> 00:43:34.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy's home! Daddy's home!</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:43:41.327 --> 00:43:44.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right. Daddy's home.</c.bg_transparent>

